issue.title: Created a Core Data ORM
issue.body: This PR adds a nice clean wrapper around Core Data MangedObject subclasses. It abstracts away a lot of the boilerplate Core Data code that is normally required. Additionally it cleans up the searching ability and mimics SQL in syntax.

issue.title: Adding XML parsing
issue.body: This PR adds in the ability to parse XML through a clean and simple interface. It is built on top of Swift's native XML parser. Lastly, it has the ability to parse out sets of XML to objects.
